# Lightning Telemetry Migrations

Place forward-only SQLite migration files for Lightning telemetry in this directory when the telemetry schema changes.

Rules:
- use zero-padded numeric prefixes such as `0002_add_quality_guard_metric.sql`
- keep migrations idempotent where possible
- do not edit already-applied migration files
- update `lightning_events_schema.sql` so fresh projects still bootstrap correctly from scratch
- rerun `uv run python tools/init_lightning_telemetry.py` after adding a migration
